text: Reza Atri Nagharchi (, born 8 August 1994 in Babol) is an Iranian freestyle wrestler. He won a Gold medal at the 2019 Asian Championship, and bronze medals at the 2017 Asian Championships and 2018 Asian Games. ==References== == External Links == * Reza Atri on Instagram * Reza Atri on Facebook Category:Living people Category:1994 births Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Wrestlers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in wrestling Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for Iran
